    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my trusty car, and it's been such a reliable companion. It's in really solid shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways! It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so while it has a bit of character from the road, it\u2019s ready to hit the pavement with its next owner. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see how great it feels behind the wheel!",
      "price": 32500.0,
